<a href="http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-02/ivorian-cocoa-reform-won-t-be-a-problem-for-barry-callebaut-1-.html" target="_self">http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-02/ivorian-cocoa-reform-won-t-be-a...</a></p><p><i>Financial Times</i>, ‘Ivorian uncertainty weights on cocoa industry’, 4 May 2012</p><p>
